        <mxCell id="flow-steps" value="1. Push code to GitHub → triggers Jenkins webhook&#xa;2. Jenkins builds, tests, scans, and pushes Docker images to ECR&#xa;3. Helm deploys to inactive environment (Blue or Green)&#xa;4. Run smoke tests on new deployment&#xa;5. Switch ALB traffic to new environment&#xa;6. Previous environment becomes standby for rollback" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1">
